name: Simple Design - Start
description:
This initiates the simple design process.

Ex. A simple logo design includes 5 concepts emailed to you for review, allowing you to submit to us any ideas for revisions. This also includes 1 round of revisions.

*For an exact idea on what package your design qualifies for, feel free to contact us above.

**This purchase is only the start of this process, the final phase must be purchased to receive the final product.

name: Simple Design - Final
description: This is the end of the simple design process. It includes 1 round of touch ups and the final product.
